- We successfully constructed `frontend/src/app/(dashboard)/governance/page.tsx` leveraging Next.js App Router and Tailwind CSS for dynamic styling. 
- Integrated directly with the frontend API service module to load `T+1` datamart records.
- **RAG Status Configuration Engine**: 
  Threshold variables (Red/Amber/Green) mapped explicitly from the requested `KPI_Matrix.csv` drive the UI's semantic colors to alert management of compliance anomalies promptly.

```typescript
// Threshold Application Engine
const getRagStatus = (value, thresholdType, boundaries) => {
  if (thresholdType === 'low_better') {
    if (value >= boundaries[1]) return { color: 'text-red-600', bg: 'bg-red-50' };
    if (value > boundaries[0]) return { color: 'text-amber-600', bg: 'bg-amber-50' };
    return { color: 'text-emerald-600', bg: 'bg-emerald-50' };
  }
  // Reverse logic applied for high_better targets
}
```

